(208, 1, '2020-03-21 20:47:33', '2020-03-21 20:47:33', '<h2>NEW HOPE</h2>		\n			<p>Empowering children of long term inmates</p>		\n			<a href=\"newhope/about/\" role=\"button\">\n						ABOUT US\n					</a>\n			<h3>Change A life</h3>		\n		<p>If you want your children to be intelligent, read them fairy tales. If you want them to be more intelligent, read them more fairy tales. Children are a great comfort to us in our old age, and they help us reach it faster too.</p>		\n			<a href=\"newhope/contact/\" role=\"button\">\n						Paticipate\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"850\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8c2842d4b05e690d5f2b597a8c7cb07689908fb6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8c2842d4b05e690d5f2b597a8c7cb07689908fb6.jpeg 850w, http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8c2842d4b05e690d5f2b597a8c7cb07689908fb6-300x181.jpeg 300w, http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8c2842d4b05e690d5f2b597a8c7cb07689908fb6-768x463.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" />											\n		<p>If we are to teach real peace in this world, and if we are to carry on a real war against war, we shall have to begin with the children.</p>		\n			<h4> — Mahatma Gandhi</h4>		\n			<h2>It\'s time to work it out </h2>		\n		<p>Safety and security don\'t just happen, they are the result of collective consensus and public investment. We owe our children, the most vulnerable citizens in our society, a life free of violence and fear.</p>		\n			<a href=\"newhope/contact/\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Us\n					</a>\n			<h3>Children need models rather than critics.</h3>		\n		<p>Children are likely to live up to what you believe of them.  We worry about what a child will become tomorrow yet we forget that he is someone today.</p>		\n										<img width=\"975\" height=\"515\" src=\"http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/charity-helping-children.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/charity-helping-children.jpg 975w, http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/charity-helping-children-300x158.jpg 300w, http://localhost/newhope/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/charity-helping-children-768x406.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 975px) 100vw, 975px\" />											\n			<a href=\"newhope/contact/\" role=\"button\">\n						Donate\n					</a>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-03-21 20:47:33', '2020-03-21 20:47:33', '', 9, 'http://localhost/newhope/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
